---
// Footer estático de Astro
---

<footer class="mt-0 border-t border-primary/10 bg-white py-20 tile-pattern">
  <div class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-16">
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <div class="size-10 bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center rounded-sm -rotate-3">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl">waves</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold italic tracking-tight text-primary">Mambbu</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm font-serif italic text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        Encuentra tu hogar ideal en Cuba. Conectamos personas con propiedades en toda la isla.
      </p>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <a class="text-primary hover:text-sea-glass transition-colors" href="#" aria-label="Sitio web">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">public</span>
        </a>
        <a class="text-primary hover:text-cuba-red transition-colors" href="#" aria-label="Instagram">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">camera</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h4 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">Explorar</h4>
      <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm font-serif italic text-gray-500">
        <li><a class="hover:text-sea-glass transition-colors" href="#">Casas y Chalets</a></li>
        <li><a class="hover:text-sea-glass transition-colors" href="#">Apartamentos</a></li>
        <li><a class="hover:text-sea-glass transition-colors" href="#">Terrenos</a></li>
        <li><a class="hover:text-sea-glass transition-colors" href="#">Propiedades de Lujo</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h4 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">Compañía</h4>
      <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm font-serif italic text-gray-500">
        <li><a class="hover:text-sea-glass transition-colors" href="#">Nuestra Historia</a></li>
        <li><a class="hover:text-sea-glass transition-colors" href="#">Agentes y Agencias</a></li>
        <li><a class="hover:text-sea-glass transition-colors" href="#">Contacto</a></li>
        <li><a class="hover:text-sea-glass transition-colors" href="#">Ayuda</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h4 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">Newsletter</h4>
      <p class="text-sm font-serif italic text-gray-500 mb-6">Recibe nuevas propiedades y ofertas directamente en tu correo.</p>
      <form class="flex">
        <input 
          class="flex-1 bg-white border-primary/20 border-r-0 py-3 px-4 text-sm italic font-serif focus:ring-0 focus:border-sea-glass" 
          placeholder="Tu correo..." 
          type="email"
          name="email"
        />
        <button type="submit" class="bg-primary text-white px-4 hover:bg-sea-glass transition-colors">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">mail</span>
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-6 mt-20 pt-8 border-t border-primary/5 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6">
    <p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400">
      © 2024 Mambbu. Portal Inmobiliario de Cuba.
    </p>
    <div class="flex gap-6 text-xs text-gray-400">
      <a class="hover:text-sea-glass transition-colors" href="#">Privacidad</a>
      <a class="hover:text-sea-glass transition-colors" href="#">Términos</a>
      <a class="hover:text-sea-glass transition-colors" href="#">Cookies</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
